description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Tom Yum Noodle Soup recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Noodle soup,Low saturated fat,High protein,Low salt,Low sugar,Low fat
name: Chicken Tom Yum Noodle Soup Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 90g Mama Shrimp (Tom Yum) Flavour instant noodles
2 bunches baby pak choy, halved crossways
1 long red chilli, thinly sliced diagonally

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium-high heat. Cook paste for 30 seconds or until fragrant. Add 2L water, 5 paste sachets from packets and 2 chilli powder sachets (add more for extra spice) from packets, then bring to the boil over high heat. Reserve any remaining sachets for another use.
Add chicken, pak choy and noodles, and cook for 2 minutes or until chicken and noodles are cooked through. Stir in lime juice. Divide soup among bowls. Top with chilli and coriander.
